Nadia Mukami has released her first 2022 single, 'Bella'. It is her first Amapiano project. "Bella means a 'beautiful woman'," she explained on Instagram. She added that the project celebrates the beauty of women. "As a young woman, I never knew there was a time I would be talking to young women on issues pregnancies, complications and motherhood journey," she said. "Women are special. I take this chance to ask you to treat your daughter, sister, wife and friend with utmost respect and sensitivity, and let’s make the world a better place." The singer thanked women for allowing her to be vulnerable with them. "I am a happy woman now, and let’s keep fighting," she said. Nadia is currently believed to be pregnant with singer Arrow Bwoy's child.